underlying_goal: The user wanted to condense a very large and verbose markdown file into a concise reference.
primary_success: Dramatically reduced a bloated 1800-line markdown file to a concise 130-line summary, making it usable.
brief_summary: The user asked to clean up a large markdown spec file. The agent identified and removed verbose tables and archived content, reducing the file size by 93%. After a user query, the agent added a clarifying note about statistical data that was not present in the original file.
